cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

The paper deals with computer vision tasks, specifically salient object detection, using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of prior models and depth cues, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed architecture also involves sub-networks, which are related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
